name: GSI Glacier Stainless JavaPress
description: Mud-free camp coffee, every time. The secret is the silicone ring plunger that eliminates any coffee "blow-by," so you won't wind up with grounds in your cup. A sturdy handle and spout make for secure pressing and pouring.Stainless steel insulated carafe.Moulded plastic handle provides a solid grip.Silicone ring plunger keeps coffee grounds and silt below the filter.Non-slip foot.976ml capacity.
